data.description: Charming home in prime location. Relax on the spacious front porch with swing. Enjoy natural woodwork and hardwood floors. Three upper bedrooms with large closets and full bath. Main level is open with cheerful sunlight exposure. Lower level offers finished square footage for family room, bath and storage or future wine cellar. 1 year HSA warranty provided to buyers at closing.
